{"text_id":140815,"tokens":["The"," rise"," of"," online"," schooling"," has"," been"," a"," significant"," development"," in"," the"," field"," of"," education",","," providing"," students"," with"," the"," flexibility"," to"," learn"," at"," their"," own"," pace"," and"," in"," their"," own"," environment","."," However",","," this"," mode"," of"," education"," also"," comes"," with"," potential"," drawbacks"," that"," can"," impact"," a"," student","'","s"," social"," development",","," academic"," performance",","," and"," future"," success"," in"," the"," real"," world",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," most"," significant"," drawbacks"," of"," online"," schooling"," is"," the"," lack"," of"," interaction"," with"," peers","."," In"," a"," traditional"," classroom"," setting",","," students"," have"," the"," opportunity"," to"," engage"," in"," face","-","to","-","face"," interactions",","," form"," relationships",","," and"," develop"," social"," skills","."," These"," interactions"," are"," crucial"," in"," building"," a"," student","'","s"," confidence",","," empathy",","," and"," communication"," skills","."," However",","," in"," an"," online"," classroom",","," students"," are"," often"," isolated"," and"," lack"," the"," social"," engagement"," that"," is"," necessary"," for"," their"," overall"," development","."," This"," lack"," of"," social"," interaction"," can"," lead"," to"," feelings"," of"," loneliness"," and"," isolation",","," which"," can"," have"," long","-","term"," effects"," on"," a"," student","'","s"," mental"," health",".","\n\n","Another"," drawback"," of"," online"," schooling"," is"," the"," absence"," of"," competition"," and"," motivation","."," In"," a"," traditional"," classroom",","," students"," are"," constantly"," competing"," with"," their"," peers",","," which"," can"," drive"," them"," to"," work"," harder"," and"," achieve"," better"," academic"," results","."," However",","," in"," an"," online"," classroom",","," student